135942dc5d980dfb1db194","tid":829263,"uid":84621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:19:24.000Z","msg":"我自己都今星期六出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd87fec4c038b73d16fc50b9e03faa24e1bc642","tid":829263,"uid":102356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"北投 溫泉博物館 維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0642b5c112a329fd334a5bcf36c68e86b44e4a2d","tid":829263,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗住咁囉D PLAN <br />\n<br />\n1 . 11:55機去到到 1500 , 台北車站 -&gt; 酒店-&gt;公館商圈- &gt;夜巿-&gt;返去<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">好鬆動嘅都，夜市唔岩考慮下書店街（如果你係睇書人），附近都好多野食</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 基隆 - &gt; 九份-&gt; 再睇下點<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">九份（連同整個菁桐綫）先，回程睇情況落基隆或者去饒河街夜市。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 陽明山 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">（有心去預大半日，回程士林一帶食下咁）</span><br />\n4. <br />\n<br />\n5. 夜機 2000 先走, 2255返到HKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有諗過烏來...又我自己一個去又好似望過D 圖唔知岩峿岩自己... 好似岩FAMILY 多D..<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">純觀光或溫泉，交通算遠，自己衡量</span><br />\n<br />\n陽明同基隆係咪斬開會比較好? 比自己REST 一日係巿中心玩好過日日出遠門<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我認為係</span><br />\n<br />\n北投溫泉有諗但唔熟.... 大家推唔推介?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b36fb330a5428a6f7c48c12526b3648c4c8c8c93","tid":829263,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"九份唔洗去.無咩好睇"},{"pid":"6954df729ea51883dee6c7dda0ef46150ac8d8f5","tid":829263,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"我黎緊都去台北<br />\n諗緊去唔去北投浸溫泉好<br />\n有冇話邊間溫泉酒店好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到一兩間靚嘅成二三千港紙晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75be6071b1b155de8545bd4845e0d2e30a63a74e","tid":829263,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6954df729ea51883dee6c7dda0ef46150ac8d8f5","tid":829263,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"我黎緊都去台北<br />\n諗緊去唔去北投浸溫泉好<br />\n有冇話邊間溫泉酒店好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到一兩間靚嘅成二三千港紙晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"之前去一間係正啲北投露天溫泉對面<br />\n好似大概1700-2700台幣個半鐘<br />\n我都想專誠由高雄坐去北投浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為高雄好似無乜邊間"}]}